flowchart TB
    subgraph Client ["Client Apps"]
        Frontend["Web Frontend\n(React SPA, CDN-served)"]
    end

    subgraph Platform ["MathBattle Platform (Containers)"]
        API["REST API\n(Node.js, NestJS)"]
        WS["WebSocket Server\n(Node.js, Socket.io)"]
        Worker["AI Worker Service\n(Node.js, BullMQ Worker)"]
        
        DB[("PostgreSQL\n(Primary & Read Replica)")]
        Redis[("Redis Cache\n(Sessions, Leaderboards, Rate Limits)")]
        Queue[("Job Queue\n(BullMQ / Redis)")]
    end

    subgraph External ["External Providers"]
        AI["AI Provider\n(OpenAI/Anthropic)"]
        Email["Email Service\n(SendGrid/Postmark)"]
        Storage["Cloud Storage\n(AWS S3/GCS)"]
    end

    Frontend -->|HTTPS API Requests| API
    Frontend -->|WebSockets Match Sessions| WS

    API -->|Reads/Writes| DB
    API -->|Cache / Rate Limit| Redis
    API -->|Enqueues Jobs| Queue

    WS -->|Checks Connection/State| Redis
    WS -->|Reads/Writes Results| DB

    Queue -->|Pipes Jobs| Worker
    Worker -->|Makes Calls| AI
    Worker -->|Writes Results| DB

    API -->|Sends Emails| Email
    API -->|Stores Uploads & Exports| Storage
